You try accessing the PDO instance (`$conn`) with `$this` outside of the class it belongs to. In a method of the Database class, you can refer to the current instance with `$this` but not outside.

You need to actually create an instance of your Database class and then access its `$conn`.

After your `include &#39;../../DAL/Database.php&#39;;`:

    $db = new Database;
    $conn = $db-&gt;conn;

Now you can use `$conn` instead of `$this-&gt;conn`.

